VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Cliff! &gt;&gt; And once again, here is Bob as Cliff. &gt;&gt; Oh, what the hell was that? &gt;&gt; You need to stay calm. What did you do? &gt;&gt; I fixed the Caylin situation.'

